Content: The configuration parameter 'yarn.timeline-service.flowname.max-size' is set to a non-positive value: -1. The flow name will not be shortened. Please set a positive integer to enable flow name shortening.
EventTemplate: The configuration parameter 'yarn.timeline-service.flowname.max-size' is set to a non-positive value: <*>. The flow name will not be shortened. Please set a positive integer to enable flow name shortening.
